FBIS3-31522 "dreeu035_b_94004" FBIS-EEU-94-035 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Feb 1994 BULGARIA Appoints National Security Chief AU1802132094 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1000 GMT 18 Feb 94 AU1802132094 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network Language: Bulgarian Article Type:BFN [Text] Today President Zhelyu Zhelev issued Decree No. 35, appointing Colonel Stefan Georgiev Dimitrov director of the National Security Service.
